# Analytical Annotations
# FIXED: Changed 'near: peer_list' to 'near: top-right' to comply with ELK constant-only near restriction
contention: |md
  **Contention Analysis:**
  - `UpdateLastSeen` dominates writer lock time.
  - `GetRandomPeers` dominates reader lock time.
  - Under 10k nodes, lock acquisition latency < 100ns.
| {
  near: top-right
  shape: text
  style: {
    font-size: 14
    italic: true
  }
}

blocking_note: |md
  ### State Transition Timeline (FIFO)
  text
  R1: [====RLock====]
  R2:     [==RLock==]     ✓ Concurrent
  R3:        [==RLock==]  ✓ Concurrent
  W1:         [--WAIT--][===Lock===]  ✗ Blocks W/R
  R4:                   [--WAIT--][RLock]
  
| {
  near: bottom-right
  shape: text
  style: {
    font: mono
    font-size: 12
    fill: "#F5F5F5"
  }
}